reportInfo.reportDetails: The science fair showcased innovative projects from students, highlighting creativity and research skills.
Students participated in various track and field events, promoting physical fitness and teamwork.
A hands-on workshop on Artificial Intelligence and Robotics was conducted by industry experts.
